      "translation": "你会知道你将幸存"
    },
    {
      "time": 137.9,
      "time_str": "02:17.900",
      "text": "So when you feel like hope is gone",
      "translation": "所以当你希望破灭时"
    },
    {
      "time": 142.3,
      "time_str": "02:22.300",
      "text": "Look inside you and be strong",
      "translation": "看着内心，学会坚强"
    },
    {
      "time": 145.98,
      "time_str": "02:25.980",
      "text": "And you'll finally see the truth",
      "translation": "你将会发现事实就是"
    },
    {
      "time": 149.81,
      "time_str": "02:29.810",
      "text": "That a hero lies in you",
      "translation": "那个英雄就是你"
    },
    {
      "time": 154.7,
      "time_str": "02:34.700",
      "text": "Lord knows......",
      "translation": "天知道"
    },
    {
      "time": 161.75,
      "time_str": "02:41.750",
      "text": "Dreams are hard to follow",
      "translation": "梦想很难实现"
    },
    {
      "time": 165.53,
      "time_str": "02:45.530",
      "text": "But don't let anyone",
      "translation": "但是不要让任何人"
    },
    {
      "time": 168.6,
      "time_str": "02:48.600",
      "text": "Tear them away",
      "translation": "破碎掉你的梦"
    },
    {
      "time": 173.55,
      "time_str": "02:53.550",
      "text": "hold on",
      "translation": "再坚持一下"
    },
    {
      "time": 177.69,
      "time_str": "02:57.690",
      "text": "There will be tomorrow",
      "translation": "还会有希望"
    },
    {
